videos.headline: McDonald hits Byrd for a 36 yard Hawai'i TD
videos.description: Hawai'I QB Cole McDonald finds a wide open Cedric Byrd II streaking for a 36 yard touchdown pass for the first score of the game.

videos.headline: Hawai'i catches Nevada sleeping with fake kneel trick play
videos.description: Cedric Byrd II runs for 29 yards and a first down off of a fake kneel down trick play for Hawai'i.
